wikipedia_page.main: Richard William "Wes" Stewart (28 February 1945 – c. 15 June 2019) was a Jamaican-born English cricketer. He played for Gloucestershire in 1966 and for Middlesex between 1966 and 1968.On 22 June 2019, it was announced that Stewart had died a week prior.
